Merge pull request #227 from airdrummingfool/appearance-transition

Use appearance transition methods on menu view controllers so that view events are sent
Adding calls to begin and end appearance transitions for the menu view controllers, so that -viewWillAppear:, -viewDidAppear:, -viewWillDisappear:, and -viewDidDisappear: are messaged.

Merge pull request #48 from iOSLabs/master

Support custom content view scale & offset when show menu

Support custom content view scale & offset when show menu

Added contentViewScaleValue, contentViewInLandscapeOffsetCenterX &
contentViewInPortraitOffsetCenterX to support defining custom scale &
offset of content view when show the menu.

In iPad landscape case, the content view will scaled to very small & the
menu's width is too wide.

Merge pull request #16 from blork/master

Refactored RESideMenu into a Custom Container View Controller
Slighty hacky fix for orientation by delaying the orientation change until after the menu has fully closed.
Fixed status bar being incorrectly hidden (white bar).
Correctly hide/show the status bar depending on property value.
Updated example to illustrate status bar changes on iOS 7.
Added category to allow 'correct' status bar style to be set, i.e. the visible view controller's.
Fixed an issue causing `preferredStatusBarStyle` to be called on the previous VC, which could cause a crash.
Fixed issue where self was retained by block.
Changed iOS 7+ method calls so that project can be run with older SDKs.

Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/romaonthego/RESideMenu

Conflicts:
	RESideMenu/RESideMenu.m
	RESideMenuExample/RESideMenuExample/RootViewController.m
Call action block rather than duplicating view controller initialisation.
In the absence of a better strategy, close the menu on rotation.
Added extra style for status bar when the menu is open - useful on iOS 7 for switching between the lightContent & default styles.
Fixed sizing of view on iOS6.
Switched orientation method (works more reliably in simulator).
Added additional properties for offsets in landscape. Added basic support for rotation, but not while the menu is visible.
Significant refactoring to change RESideMenu into a Custom Container View Controller. Views are therefore no longer added directly to the window, allowing the menu to respond to rotation callbacks.
